- **Independent Repository**: This is a separate git repository from the main project
- **Remote**: https://github.com/lab22poland/netolib.git
- **Purpose**: Core networking utilities and libraries for the NETo suite

## Development Focus
- **Library Development**: Reusable networking components
- **Platform Independence**: Code should work across iOS, macOS, and potentially other platforms
- **API Design**: Clean, well-documented public interfaces

## Library Characteristics
- **Modular Design**: Well-defined modules for different networking functions
- **Documentation**: Comprehensive API documentation required
- **Testing**: Extensive unit test coverage for all public APIs
- **Dependencies**: Minimal external dependencies preferred

